{"tha-ap212:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap212:0.2":"Kanikarapupphiyavagga ","tha-ap212:0.3":"10 Papanivariyattheraapadana ","tha-ap212:1.1":"“Tissassa tu bhagavato, ","tha-ap212:1.2":"devadevassa tadino; ","tha-ap212:1.3":"Ekacchattam maya dinnam, ","tha-ap212:1.4":"vippasannena cetasa. ","tha-ap212:2.1":"Nivutam hoti me papam, ","tha-ap212:2.2":"kusalassupasampada; ","tha-ap212:2.3":"Akase chattam dharenti, ","tha-ap212:2.4":"pubbakammassidam phalam. ","tha-ap212:3.1":"Carimam vattate mayham, ","tha-ap212:3.2":"bhava sabbe samuhata; ","tha-ap212:3.3":"Dharemi antimam deham, ","tha-ap212:3.4":"sammasambuddhasasane. ","tha-ap212:4.1":"Dvenavute ito kappe, ","tha-ap212:4.2":"yam chattamadadim tada; ","tha-ap212:4.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap212:4.4":"chattadanassidam phalam. ","tha-ap212:5.1":"Dvesattatimhito kappe, ","tha-ap212:5.2":"atthasimsu janadhipa; ","tha-ap212:5.3":"Mahanidananamena, ","tha-ap212:5.4":"rajano cakkavattino. ","tha-ap212:6.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap212:6.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap212:6.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap212:7.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma papanivariyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap212:8.1":"Papanivariyattherassapadanam dasamam. ","tha-ap212:9.1":"Kanikarapupphiyavaggo ekavisatimo. ","tha-ap212:10.1":"Tassuddanam ","tha-ap212:11.1":"Kanikaro minelanca, ","tha-ap212:11.2":"kinkani taranena ca; ","tha-ap212:11.3":"Niggundipupphi dakado, ","tha-ap212:11.4":"salalo ca kurandako; ","tha-ap212:11.5":"Adharako papavari, ","tha-ap212:11.6":"atthatalisa gathakati. "}